# Development Workflow

## Quick Start

```bash
# Docker
docker-compose up -d

# Manual
cd backend && npm run dev  # Port 3001
cd frontend && npm run dev # Port 5173
```

## Development Commands

```bash
# Backend
cd backend && npm run dev
cd backend && npm test
cd backend && npm run lint

# Frontend
cd frontend && npm run dev
cd frontend && npm test
cd frontend && npm run lint
```

## Database Management

```bash
cd backend/scripts
./print-all-characters.sh    # View all characters
./search-character.sh "name" # Search characters
./database-stats.sh         # Database statistics
./reset-database.sh         # Reset database
```

## Project Structure

- **Backend**: Express API (port 3001)
- **Frontend**: React app (port 5173)
- **Database**: SQLite (`backend/data/characters.db`)
- **Scripts**: `backend/scripts/` for database operations
